Abduction.desc: Chance that a xeno enemy gains Deathtouch.

Angel Barrier.desc: Chance to create a shield that only prevents damage from righteous opponents.

Angelbane.desc: Increases your damage against Archangel enemies.

Angels' Wrath.desc: Chance to deal massive holy damage at the beginning of combat.

Angelward.desc: Damage taken from Archangel enemies is reduced.

Apocalypse.desc: Chance to remove several opposing Retainers from combat.

Arcane Fire.desc: Chance to apply a strong mystic damage-over-time (DOT) effect. DOTs deal damage every round.

Arcane Sunburst.desc: Chance to deal additional mystic damage-over-time (DOT) against vampiric creatures. DOTs deal damage every round.

Attraction.desc: Increases your chance to encounter rarer non-boss enemies.
